<h3>Disability Line</h3>
<p>
<a class="resource" href="http://www.ayjnihh.nic.in/disabilityline.htm">http://www.ayjnihh.nic.in/disabilityline.htm</a><br />
Provides information on diagnosis, treatment, counseling, education, employment, neighborhood service facilities, government schemes, and facilities related to  disabilities round the clock.
</p>

<h3>Taxes and Duties</h3>
<p>
